s/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cae90f73e796e6b9e03c66b083538f7cdfa337","tid":126164,"uid":3926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fc5fead8ad778a022723a19ee97be7ab39acd51","tid":126164,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"利申: 英文差<br />\n未試過用呢個方法記英文既野<br />\n等巴絲出黎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf188af7eaf70ce63958f4d515240ab72a2845a","tid":126164,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"背書,不了"},{"pid":"9b6cca38c0d485d698f9715a6f5156b881597878","tid":126164,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"我詳細分享下我個方法先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次可以揀一條自己熟既路，例如屋企附近。<br />\n之後將你要背既野分拆，再逐個逐個「套用」沿途既「check point」。<br />\n「套用」即係將你要背既句子詞語誇大到9唔搭8，再塞落check point到。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例: 复溜穴 交信穴 築賓穴《腎經某幾穴》<br />\n复溜，可以想像成為<span style=\"color: red;\">中年人發褔，好似溜兵緊</span>。例如套用係日本城出面既走廊地下度，你感覺行行下個地下突然拱起來，而且好滑，質地好似中年人既肚腩咁。<br />\n<br />\n交信，可以想像為<span style=\"color: red;\">膠制的信件</span>，套用係升降機門口度，你可以想像有個郵差有一大袋既膠信，督穿個袋，d信全部跌哂出黎，堆積如山咁，阻住你搭lift。<br />\n<br />\n築賓，可以想像為<span style=\"color: red;\">小學雞係度玩捉賓周遊戲</span>，套用係橋頭度。你可以想像d欄杆地下，全部都係賓周，d細路係咁鬥快捉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要注意既地方：<br />\n1 唔好重覆用checkpoint記唔同野。<br />\n2 條路線最好簡單，直接。<br />\n3 唔建議用樓層做路線，會奶野，超亂(試過。<br />\n4 唔好想像條路線，要腳踏實地咁出去行。<br />\n5 唔好將checkpoint集中得大密，又或者隔幾條街。<br />\n6 下一日必須複習一次(可以唔駛實地複習)。<br />\n7 以上既「故事」最好自己想像，唔好記人地諗出黎既野。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就咁舉個例好似冇乜效果咁，你試下親身用，會唔同好多。<br />\n<br />\n初入者用背完應該個人好攰好攰，但係你過左呢個期，就會習慣。<br />\n<br />\n同埋入門既話<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議</span>拆成詞語咁背，之後再慢慢咁延伸到背句子，然後文章。"},{"pid":"4a3046e984065d276c888979d37ecd29f524be97","tid":126164,"uid":33995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"有無記公式方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理科jj留名"},{"pid":"caf9402d129edf5b93080a01e751661649f47de0","tid":126164,"uid":3926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5644aec09ec93011dc7da306785f65e387f1b6cd","tid":126164,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無記公式方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理科jj留名</blockquote><br />\n公式我又未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry巴打 <br />\n同求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03fe15ae3e7f460a78e39ac19b1b230531ff710","tid":126164,"uid":6957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm <br />\n原來以前溫中史有用過memory palace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家仲有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依加少咗 再用返先<br />\n我要好專心先得<br />\n我成日專心唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熄電話會心思思開返<br />\n個腦不停諗其他嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b86e8508b9eb5871802124c14a8fbd379d5f80b","tid":126164,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪要搵好多條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上係<br />\n但係如果你地圖用得熟，你可以用好多野代替，例如google街景(建議cap圖做record)，<br />\n或者憑空作故事(呢樣好易唔記得)<br />\n我fd用gta地圖記憶，都會記到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8fe40b6ef5d4ebea5cfa1e7359708866c646a6","tid":126164,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"真心唔會背書，靠理解<br />\n<br />\n明左背後原因就自然記到，利申: 工程撚"}]}